  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="bg-[#F5F5F0]">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 md:py-16 max-w-4xl">

      <div class="bg-navy/5 border-l-4 border-gold rounded-r-lg p-4 mb-6">
        <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed italic">Dolphin Centrifuge provides disc stack centrifuge installation guidance and turnkey system commissioning for all DMPX and DMB series systems. Proper installation — including foundation clearances, piping design, and utility connections — prevents over 80% of common operational issues. Based in Warren, Michigan, Dolphin Centrifuge has over 40 years of experience in centrifuge system installation and startup.</p>
