            <li><a href="#centrifuge-location-in-relation-to-accessory-tanks" class="text-[#1B3A5C] hover:text-[#E8A317] transition">Centrifuge Location In Relation To Accessory Tanks</a></li>
            <li><a href="#location-of-electrical-control-system" class="text-[#1B3A5C] hover:text-[#E8A317] transition">Location of Electrical Control System</a></li>
            <li><a href="#piping" class="text-[#1B3A5C] hover:text-[#E8A317] transition">Piping</a></li>
            <li><a href="#utilities" class="text-[#1B3A5C] hover:text-[#E8A317] transition">Utilities</a></li>
